evilvte
	requires gtk
	sometimes stops the output
		https://bugzilla.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi?id=726235
	slow
urxvt
	mouse is borked after killing vim, reset(1) doesn't work
		fixed by `printf '\e[?1000l\e[?1002l\e[?1003l\e[?1004l\e[?1006l'`
	unusual and unclear custom font substitution machinery
xterm
	loses the buffer contents on shrinking the window
	impossible to select more than a screenful of symbols
st
	mouse is permanently borked after killing vim, reset(1) doesn't work
	doesn't provide a scrollback buffer
kitty
	can't utilize bitmap fonts
		https://sw.kovidgoyal.net/kitty/faq/#kitty-is-not-able-to-use-my-favorite-font
konsole
	pulls kde
	positions characters from different fonts in a fucked up way
	treats empty space after a line ends as spaces during selection/copying
	copying stuff sometimes misses symbols (todo/timed)
terminology
	slow
	comes with mandatory animations
alacritty
	doesn't work on old video cards
	uses cargo
sakura
	has no contrast palette option and the maintainer have rejected the PR adding the ability to customize it
		https://code.launchpad.net/~kyleb/sakura/custom-palette/+merge/73968
gnome-console
	can't turn off the window decorations
		https://tinystash.undef.im/il/3JPCpNWmkBqocJ655XXAQkmk7mQLyujTuAc557QfXRUH3gawnvA2iAQ7zXcuheF52NPGKWE6KTV2RVemkYqYjcph.png
